.</p></div><div><p><b>Closing:</b></p><!-- --><p>Hangup logic, fallbacks and goodbyes.</p></div></div></div><div id=\"features\"><div><p>Enterprise-grade by default</p></div><div><div><p>Identity, conversation and closing blocks with checklists.</p></div><div><p>Compliance friendly checks for all sectors on by default.</p></div><div><p>Handles all edge cases, instead of just linear scripts.</p></div><div><p>Auto-picks the best TTS &amp; STT models for each use case.</p></div><div><p>Warm endings and fallbacks for smooth user experiences.</p></div><div><p>Thousands of proven templates applied across sectors.</p></div></div></div><div id=\"book\"><p>Contact us</p></div></div></DIV>","content_text":"HomeLive agentsInside StudioEnterprise gradeBook demoLive on Product HuntUpvote usTrained onVoice AI CallsVoice AgentsExpert HoursTry Agent Studio Talk to a live agentSaanviHR Executive RecruitmentSonalEducation Counsellor EdTechAnikaCustomer Support Executive E-commerceInside Agent StudioAgent Studio captures the identity, conversation and closing to sketch the skeleton of the agent and fills the remaining gaps, flows, and guardrails from an extensive module library.Identity:Define personality, voice and tone.Conversation:Flow, edge-cases and guardrails.Closing:Hangup logic, fallbacks and goodbyes.Enterprise-grade by defaultIdentity, conversation and closing blocks with checklists.Compliance friendly checks for all sectors on by default.Handles all edge cases, instead of just linear scripts.Auto-picks the best TTS & STT models for each use case.Warm endings and fallbacks for smooth user experiences.Thousands of proven templates applied across sectors.Contact us","fetched_at":"2026-07-24T06:57:17.131Z","ok":true,"blocks":[{"html_en":"<p><span>Trained on</span></p>","sentences":[{"en":"Trained on","zh":"受训于"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Voice AI Calls</span></p>","sentences":[{"en":"Voice AI Calls","zh":"语音人工智能通话"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Voice Agents</span></p>","sentences":[{"en